name: Souvenirs From The Sun - Gijs van den Berg

metadata.name: Souvenirs From The Sun #1
metadata.description:
This photograph is part of the series 'Souvenirs From The Sun' by artist Gijs van den Berg

Edition 1/1
4611 x 6917 px

Souvenirs From The Sun was nominated for the Sony World Photography Awards 2017 and presented in full as a solo exhibition at The Print Space Gallery in London.
